cat << EOF
The most global class is Project. It is a singleton so all data that can be 
shared among KAider instances should go into it.

KAider is a dispatcher for one catalog editing window.
KAiderView is msgid/msgstr viewer/editor.
All specialized actions should go into views (QDockWidgets).
